<Document>
	<name>Topcastles: Top 100 of Medieval Castles </name>
	<open>1</open>
	<Snippet maxLines="1">topkastelen_earth.xls</Snippet>
	<description>Topcastles according to http://www.topcastles.com.
The bigger the icon the higher the score of the castle. 
July 11th, 2011.

© 2004-2011 Robert Rongen: 
The content of this work and the pictures taken by Robert Rongen are licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial 3.0 Unported License. 
© Other pictures: Copyright reserved by photographer marked on the picture.</description>
	<LookAt>
		<longitude>9.27553021417601</longitude>
		<latitude>47.2593</latitude>
		<altitude>0</altitude>
		<heading>0</heading>
		<tilt>0</tilt>
		<range>2000000</range>
	</LookAt>
